pkgmetadata.longdescription: Supplemental U. S. 2010 Census Tract Boundaries for 23 Eastern States without Registries for 'SeerMapper' // Provides supplemental 2010 census tract boundary package for 23 states without Seer Registries that are east of the Mississippi river for use with the 'SeerMapper' package. The data contained in this package is derived from U. S. Census data and is in public domain.
